{"tid":500374,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［解放腦力潛能］終極1q題","createTime":"2017-12-15T16:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T12:16:04.000Z","uid":79870,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6eda977147d2b98c701cb7a148fbdf4ec51dec0f","tid":500374,"uid":79870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T16:59:01.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>「聽聞...只有iq過百的人才能解開這道題目」[/red]</span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小明係一個好窮既人，三餐不繼溫飽。平日露宿街頭，藉著行乞為生，生活狀況十分悽慘。某日，佢因為一件意外失去咗一隻耳仔。但係小明對此不屑一顧，因為世俗煩囂既聲音對佢嚟講係一種折磨。<br />\n<br />\n不知何故地，有人捐咗一隻耳仔比小明，佢又獲得返健全既聽力。小明竟然感到十分開心，但係可怕既係，佢開心的原因並不在於能夠回復聽力，而是......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>[i]<span style=\"font-size: small;\"> 「We have two ears and one mouth, so we should listen more than we say.」<br />\n</span></em></strong></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"> Zeno of Citium</span></strong></em></div>"},{"pid":"78cdac2928f08167ef5cb524f4699926a1384f61","tid":500374,"uid":79870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T17:00:04.000Z","msg":"請問為什麼小明會感到開心呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e78b3a3d8fdd82d288b88e5c2c4c267c6387e579","tid":500374,"uid":26771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T17:01:52.000Z","msg":"因為「有耳的光彩」<br />\n此po已完"},{"pid":"c28dfaf0642f30a4a391ec63ddd7e7f257c8aa84","tid":500374,"uid":79870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T17:03:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為「有耳的光彩」<br />\n此po已完</blockquote><br />\n錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c927203c6bee5ba650ae45ee3d34cf20e3071f","tid":500374,"uid":114072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T17:06:43.000Z","msg":"可以戴耳筒?"},{"pid":"f402d99129a0dfc43a2dfef81b5b48fcb57a982d","tid":500